_sText:
Here is my latest version of my map
**Jb_carceris**, and probaly the last BETA!

**And I really need feedback on this one! As this might be the last BETA.** 

Bz2 version can be found [here](http://www.gamemaps.nl/versluis/cstrike/maps/jb_carceris_beta09.bsp.bz2 "Bz2 Link")

This is just a next version of the BETA, added a few more things (Check changelog) and packed some missing textures.

Note that this is a Beta, next version will be much better. (Will add **HDR** and **bigger lightmaps!**)

In this classic map there can be found:

- Soccer
 - Airball (NEW!)
 - Anti Gravity
 - Dodgeball
 - Big ball
 - Regular soccer
- Disco
- Pool
 - Waterpolo
 - Diving
 - Jump rope
- LR
 - Gun Toss
 - Arena
 - Shot 4 Shot
- Yard one
 - Hot Potato
 - 4 in a row
 - Jumping contest
 - Pacman (NEW!)
- Yard two
 - Simon says
 - Race


Changelog:

- Deleted Skate
- Added "Pacman"
- Added a few more secrets
- Updated soccer 
- Added more features to soccer
- Balanced some secrets
- Vent enlarged
- Medic at soccer
- Added a few more "easter-egg radios"
- Updated jail section


The map itself is fully optimized, and not heavy for any server at all.

For any suggestions or feedback, please reply!
Or contact me via Gamebanana or [Steam](http://steamcommunity.com/id/DoctorWafflez "Steam Account")!
